This is Parish Plate — a Catholic Lenten fish fry directory and online ordering app for St. Louis.

Stack: Next.js (App Router), Supabase, Vercel, Resend
Live URL: https://fish-fry-finder-qab8.vercel.app (rebranding to parishplate.com)
GitHub: https://github.com/greinerbstl-letsgitit/fish-fry-finder
Contact: Brett Greiner, greinerbstl@gmail.com

DB tables: locations, events, menu_items, orders, order_items, admins, entree_sides, claim_requests

Key features: public directory (search by city/zip/parish), location approval system, 
claim-your-listing flow, online ordering with cart + toast notifications, Order Now button 
grays out outside event hours, ordering optional per location, super admin dashboard, 
email via Resend.

Env vars: NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL, NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY, RESEND_API_KEY, 
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL, SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY